<br>
Speed dropping when I'm not in combat.  Tonight in the 3rd Batlleground I was in a full group with two skalds.  On three occasions over a 2 hour period of RvR'n, we noticed speed drop for us when not in combat at least twice.  Both of us had Speed song up the whole time, so it happened even with both our songs up and both of us in range...<br>
<br>
The specific time I remember this happening, we were chasing down a fleeing Alb.  I was in the lead and he was a good ways behind me.  I do my Snare Shout and it lands on the fleeing alb.  As I expected, my speed song dropped.  Seconds later I get a confirming /tell from him saying that his speed song had dropped as soon as I hit my Snare shout.<br>
<br>
To my knowledge, it is not supposed to work that way...  And if it is, grrrr...  =)<br>
<br>
&lt;Missing Damage Add Pulses&gt;<br>
<br>
I have not been able to confirm this one in RvR yet.  But in PvE there has been MANY occasions where my very first hit on a mob does not have the damage add applied.  I am not in the middle of any shouts and the Damage Add songs has been constantly on.  I have not noticed this happening on any other hit than the first...<br>
<br>
I will post a couple of screen shots of the other skald confirming when this happens when I get a chance.  While I cant find a specific cause, at least it seems to be consistant and affect the whole group and not just individuals...<br>
<br>
Well, these are my findings and I would love to see these corrected.  =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/uedgruberman.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ed Gruberman</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Participant</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#ff0000>(9/30/02 3:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=341.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Speed Dropping and Missing Damage Add Pulses...</span><hr size=1> I haven't played much since the patch, but one of the few times I did I noticed the missing damage add on the first strike.<br>
